Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.68,0:00:23.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu Pendeta Shoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia gemetar?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.61,0:00:33.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoriko.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.82,0:00:34.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikut aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.03,0:00:36.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, Tuan Sogen.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia putrinya pria yang mati disantet itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.87,0:00:44.50,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku harus menyelidiki ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.58,0:00:45.75,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku setuju.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.67,0:00:47.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otoya?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.25,0:00:51.55,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Tuan Mao khawatir kau bertindak sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kau datang!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, apa rencananya?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.89,0:01:02.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami menemukan boneka kutukan\Nterkubur di gerbang korban.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.27,0:01:05.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti melakukan semacam ritual.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekang semua iblis!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.25,0:01:31.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko, Yoriko sudah datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoriko,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,kenapa kau gemetar?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.51,0:01:36.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku…
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.63,0:01:40.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau takut padaku, Yoriko?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.77,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Tidak sama sekali. Aku takkan pernah…
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.56,0:01:48.35,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya mendapat penglihatan…
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.40,0:01:52.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,tentang sisa umur ayahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggallah di ordo kami, Yoriko.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.99,0:01:59.16,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.16,0:02:02.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya ini bukan yang pertama kali.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.12,0:02:09.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu soal orang tua pengikut\Nyang meninggal?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.92,0:02:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Begitu sebatang kara,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.34,0:02:16.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,mereka menyumbangkan harta warisan\Nkepada ordo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sama saja merampas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa dibilang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoriko, kau harus istirahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak, Tuan Sogen.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok, kita akan urus formalitasnya
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.23,0:02:34.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk memindahkan\Nhak dojo ayahmu kepada ordo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.82,0:02:35.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paham?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kutanya pada dewa iblis,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.69,0:04:39.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia bilang tak mengutuk ayahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.74,0:04:46.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayahmu menyebut\NPendeta Shoko penipu, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sebabnya dia kena azab.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berusaha meyakinkan ayahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin menyelamatkannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyelamatkannya
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,dari ramalan kematian?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhenti!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Sogen, iblis apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa. Hanya ilusi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lebih mencemaskan Yoriko.\NPasti ada masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar, Nona Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.24,0:05:35.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benda apa itu, Otoya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.66,0:05:38.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Mao menyuruhnya membantu kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.46,0:05:42.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pecahan dewa iblis dari boneka kutukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, fungsinya seperti alat komunikasi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemunculan dewa iblis\Nmembuktikan kutukannya nyata.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan ulah amatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.47,0:05:55.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari mana asal mantranya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruang bawah tanah rahasia?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,salinan manuskrip.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Isinya banyak mantra.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.59,0:06:32.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, Pendeta Shoko mengutuk\Npakai buku ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya dia mengikuti\Npetunjuk di dalamnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, umur...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.73,0:06:42.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya Pendeta Shoko bisa mengatur\Numur sesukanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada mantra pengubah umur di situ?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.69,0:06:49.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada. Isinya cuma kutukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita terkunci!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf mengganggu, Tenko.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.80,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Tapi boleh kutanya siapa dia, Dokter Mao?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.60,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dia putrinya pria yang mati disantet itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.02,0:07:17.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namanya Yoriko.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jaga dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.98,0:07:23.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obat itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya bisa menyingkirkan roh jahat
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menghapus kutukan ayahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesampainya di rumah,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,kucampur obat itu ke dalam sake Ayah
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menyuruhnya minum.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.84,0:07:52.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi nyawanya tetap tak tertolong.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Buka pintunya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau melakukan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Buka sekarang juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percuma, pintunya terlalu berat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otoya, apa ada jalan keluar lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Nanoka, lihat ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pintu lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengarah makin ke bawah?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuharap jalan ini tembus ke luar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.76,0:08:30.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanah?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bau busuk apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau turun ke sana?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pinjam ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk apa sekop?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menemukan ini, Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tengkorak manusia?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawa Yoriko kembali!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaga ketat dojo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Geledah area ini sampai tuntas!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, Tuan Sogen.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sogen.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa dengan Yoriko?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang perlu dicemaskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan kembali ke kamar Anda.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau takkan memberitahuku apa pun, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.27,0:09:33.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu saat masih kecil,\Npenglihatanku jauh lebih tajam.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari letak dompet yang hilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,akhir tragis pemabuk kronis,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,sampai keberadaan gadis yang kawin lari.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awalnya kami hanya buka praktik\Nramalan kecil-kecilan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko, ada yang meminta petunjuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.71,0:09:51.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,seiring bertambahnya usiaku,\Npenglihatan itu memudar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.18,0:10:00.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi pengikut kami makin banyak\Ndan ordo ini membesar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.81,0:10:06.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kini, satu-satunya\Nyang bisa kulihat hanyalah
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,hari kiamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di bawah gudang, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya terbuka!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suaramu berisik sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Mao…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewa iblis menuntunku kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya aku datang lebih awal?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tepat! Kau terlambat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang tak beres dengan sekte ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami menemukan jasad setidaknya tiga orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang menggalinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.69,0:11:00.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pergi sebentar, Tuan Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di gudang bawah tanah,\Naku menemukan manuskrip ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, dari sinilah
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,kutukan itu menyebar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang apa kalian di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona, kau pengikut baru kemarin, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.86,0:11:36.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria ini orang nomor dua di sekte ini\Natau semacamnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nomor dua?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Kita bertemu kemarin.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manuskrip ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari mana kau mendapatkannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.54,0:11:51.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat muda, aku mempelajari ilmu rahasia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu? Manuskrip itu dipercayakan padamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mencurinya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.84,0:12:04.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu keahlianmu, 'kan, Sogen?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong mundur, Pendeta Shoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku yang mengurus penyusup ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kutanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.03,0:12:25.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko, kau pernah bertemu Byoki?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Byoki?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya kau bisa mengatur\Numur manusia sesukamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak punya kekuatan semacam itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah! Dia mengakuinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah Yoriko mati sesuai ramalanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.35,0:12:53.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu karena kau yang menyantetnya, Sogen.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Tuan Sogen?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti mempelajarinya\Ndari manuskrip itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.94,0:13:04.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi mewujudkan ramalan Pendeta Shoko?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku pernah berlatih ilmu rahasia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong hentikan kegilaan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.91,0:13:17.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa. Aku takkan membiarkan\Nmereka pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Termasuk aku dan Otoya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.67,0:13:24.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami berdua tahu terlalu banyak rahasia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.18,0:13:29.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kukirim santet untuk membunuh kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak tahu seberapa mengerikannya\Nkutukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namamu Sogen, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menyantet ayah Yoriko demi mewujudkan
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,ramalan Pendeta Shoko, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo pulang, Yoriko!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan begini, Ayah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau wanita itu benar-benar orang sakti
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.04,0:13:58.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang bisa mengatur umur sesukanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,coba suruh dia membunuhku\Ndengan kesaktiannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga hari…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umurmu tinggal tiga hari lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menghabisinya
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan santet Enmi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enmi?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada di manuskrip itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.48,0:14:21.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ilmu santet menggunakan boneka korban.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mirip ritual boneka jerami?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cukup paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk kasus ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.49,0:14:32.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,boneka kutukannya ditanam\Ndi gerbang rumah korban.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.87,0:14:36.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anggota keluarga yang menginjaknya\Nakan kena kutukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Usahamu nyaris berhasil.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.96,0:14:43.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya kau salurkan\Nlebih banyak energi pada mantranya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu dewa iblis kutukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga bisa mengendalikannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan tertipu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ilusi itu tak mempan padaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak paham, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini boneka kutukan yang kau tanam.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.71,0:15:23.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini dewa iblismu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewa iblisku?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi santetku berhasil?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia malah kegirangan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau berlatih ilmu rahasia
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menemukan buku santet terlarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.89,0:15:40.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau hanya perlu
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyalurkan lebih banyak energi\Nke dalam kutukanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang melahirkan dewa iblis itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku fokus, aku bisa mengendalikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.95,0:15:50.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu…
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Majulah, Dewa Iblisku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Santet penyusup ini sampai mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sogen…
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia termakan omonganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terlambat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mengekang dewa iblis ini
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan sekarang dia tunduk padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kukembalikan dia padamu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lewat mantra balasan,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku melepaskan dewa iblis ini\Ndan mengembalikan kutukannya padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang baru saja terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Sogen…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.66,0:16:38.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tolong…\N- Aku takkan buka mulut…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Roh jahat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian sudah gila, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hantu keji!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bicara dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak melihat siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.63,0:16:53.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti melihat\Nroh para korban yang dia kubur.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.22,0:16:58.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beberapa pengikut paling setia kami\Nmendadak hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah orang tuanya tiada,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.48,0:17:06.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,mereka menyumbangkan\Nsemua harta warisan ke ordo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau memercayainya, tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau membunuh mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.83,0:17:21.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau membunuh pengikut kita\Nbeserta orang tuanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia turun tangan sendiri\Nkalau santetnya gagal?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa jadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka pelakunya!\NMereka yang meracuni orang tua sendiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau yang memberikan racunnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat melewati halaman,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku melihat tanaman janda merana,\Nbakung lembah,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,oleander, dan upas puan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Taman ini
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,penuh tanaman beracun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.48,0:17:52.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tak membuktikan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulut dewa iblis telah merasukimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulut itu dipenuhi kekuatan\Ndari mantra kutukanmu sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.21,0:18:09.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulut itu hanya bisa berkata jujur.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua perbuatanmu akan terbongkar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau berani menyantet orang,\Nbersiaplah menanggung akibatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu niat jahatmu tercium,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,kutukan itu akan berbalik padamu\Nberkali-kali lipat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.18,0:18:27.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kutukan bukan mainan untuk orang awam.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah… Sudahlah…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Mereka ayah dan anak?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyerahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga akan menyerahkan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,umur ayah takkan lama lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami menemukan mayat manusia!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata laporannya benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat jalan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa Pendeta Shoko ikut ditangkap?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.85,0:19:12.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia memang penipu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya!\NSegera tinggalkan Ibu Kota Kekaisaran!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari kiamat akan segera tiba!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bumi akan terbelah,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan tornado api\Nakan meluluhlantakkan Ibu Kota!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.00,0:19:29.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Diam!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhenti meracuni pikiran warga\Ndengan bualanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Jangan-jangan…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau dibebaskan, Yoriko?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku memberi ayahku racun dari Ordo
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,karena mengira itu obat,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi aku menyerahkan diri ke polisi, tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obat yang kuberikan pada Yoriko\Nadalah obat penenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah dia menidurkan ayahnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku menyusup masuk lalu\Nmenyuntikkan racun mematikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia bertindak sejauh itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebelumnya, ada pengikut\Nyang panik saat melihat
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.66,0:20:11.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang tuanya sekarat keracunan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.62,0:20:15.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu hampir membongkar semuanya.\NJadi ini untuk antisipasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.92,0:20:20.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka mungkin ingin membuat seolah-olah\NYoriko yang meracuni ayahnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.51,0:20:23.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,agar mereka bisa membungkamnya\Ndengan rasa bersalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi pengikut yang tak tahan
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.97,0:20:29.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan mencoba melapor, malah dibunuh
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu dikubur.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.60,0:20:36.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Pendeta Shoko benar-benar dukun palsu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih percaya padanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.48,0:20:45.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melihat sendiri tubuhnya bersinar\Nsaat menyembuhkan bayi yang sakit!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, Nona Nanoka juga bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.16,0:20:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Trik apa yang dia pakai?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia menaruh senter\Ndi dalam botol sake, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.83,0:20:58.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kata Nanoka, ruangannya penuh asap\Ndan bau dupa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu trik tabir asap.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu dengan menyalakan senter\Ndi waktu yang pas,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.47,0:21:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,terciptalah efek cahaya mistis.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.18,0:21:16.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi saat itu,\NPendeta Shoko sedang menggendong si bayi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin ibu bayi itu sekongkolannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.78,0:21:23.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia yang menyalakan senternya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko pasti diatur oleh Tuan Sogen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa selama ini aku sangat buta?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.54,0:21:38.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya bukan kau yang membunuh ayahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah Sogen tak membunuhmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas bantuan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.64,0:21:47.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Oh!\N- Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sampai kau jatuh hati\Npada Dokter Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.68,0:21:54.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.64,0:21:56.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seleranya terlalu tinggi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.52,0:21:58.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.69,0:22:05.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah sudah berapa hari\Nsejak aku pergi ke dunia sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.87,0:22:10.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.91,0:22:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.41,0:22:14.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata baru sejam berlalu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.37,0:22:19.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Konsep waktunya benar-benar aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.84,0:22:23.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gempa Besar Kanto…
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.80,0:22:24.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cari.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.18,0:22:30.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Pada tanggal 1 September 1923,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.85,0:22:32.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,pukul 11.58."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.56,0:22:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Gempa bumi besar terjadi."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.73,0:22:37.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Karena itu waktu makan siang,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.98,0:22:41.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,kebakaran langsung terjadi\Ndi lebih dari seratus lokasi."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Karena ditiup angin kencang,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,apinya menyebar, menciptakan tornado api,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.78,0:22:51.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan 43 persen Kota Tokyo lama hancur."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.45,0:22:53.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tornado api…
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.29,0:22:58.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tornado api akan meluluhlantakkan ibu kota!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.25,0:23:02.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ramalan Pendeta Shoko benar-benar terjadi…
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.25,0:23:04.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengerikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.46,0:23:07.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanggal 1 September 1923…
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.22,0:23:09.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahun itu sama dengan
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.59,0:23:11.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Era Taisho di dunia sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.47,0:23:14.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti tak lama lagi…
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.39,0:23:17.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gempa Besar Kanto.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.11,0:24:50.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gempa Besar Kanto terjadi
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.57,0:24:52.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,pukul 11.58
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.53,0:24:54.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,pada tanggal 1 September.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:54.95,0:24:58.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tragedi jalan ambles yang menimpaku\Nterjadi di tanggal yang sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.58,0:25:01.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebuah bangunan ala Barat yang ganjil\Nberdiri di lokasi
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.87,0:25:04.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,warga mengabadikan batu kunci.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.29,0:25:07.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mao, kami sudah lama menunggumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.75,0:25:09.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menjadikanku umpan?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:09.67,0:25:12.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, aku cuma bisa mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:12.26,0:25:14.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benci kau, Mao!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:15.01,0:25:17.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya, "Batu Kunci".
